               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420509-name-866" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-866" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-866" type="surname" value="SELLERS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-866" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SELLERS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am porter at the National Debt Office, in the Old Jewry. About twelve o'clock, on the 11th of May, I was in the office—I saw the prisoner coming to the door—as I was going to the door, he took a wire guard from the window and ran down the steps with it—I ran after him and collared him—he had the guard under his arm—I de<lb></lb>sired him to come back to the office—he immediately dropped the guard, and escaped from me—I took it up and ran, crying, "Stop thief"—I never lost sight of him till he was stopped in Bell-alley—the policeman came up, and I gave him into custody—this is the guard—it is the property of her Majesty—the National Debt Office belong to the Crown.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
