                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-867" type="given" value="ABRAHAM"></interp>ABRAHAM DAVY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a City police-constable. I took the prisoner in charge with the guard.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was coming down the Old Jewry; I saw a man like a porter run down the steps with the guard; he threw it at my feet; I picked it up; the prosecutor collared me, and in the sudden effort of his tearing my shirt I ran away.</p>
